{
  "stem": "4963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Schmuel and some other big [INAUDIBLE] there, and they-- we-- we tried to, you know, bribe them with this, with that, and telling them all you were not going to gain anything by-- by sending us off into prisons.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why don't-- we will give you all this and let us go?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which they finally did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so again, my lucky star was above me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went through to Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was another-- no, no, the truck left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That truck that took us to the woods, he-- he-- he turned around and went back to court Kaunas.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we-- we smuggled ourselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to walk through the woods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the borders were very-- very simple.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, you know, we-- there was no gate, or maybe there was a fence in some parts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- however, where the headquarters of-- for the Russian police was, that was-- that was Lithuanian on one side and the other side was Poland, on the other side of the woods.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we trespassed the wood-- the woods and when they let us go, they said, all right, go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we took a train from there into Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then from Warsaw, we took the train into Lodz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there I-- we had to stay there until we were going into Munich.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you mention about if I was ever sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, there I came down with the measles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "With chicken pox.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Chicken pox?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Let me see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No, measles.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Measles.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I remember that in those days, you felt that you couldn't-- when you had measles everything had to be in a dark situation, in a dark, closed environment.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there were drapes and there were-- there were shutters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Schmuel stayed with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
